<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Portfolio | VIT CSE</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body { background: #0f172a; color: white; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .glass { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
        .gradient-text { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #818cf8); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-6 md:p-12">
    <header class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16 text-center md:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">I'm <span class="gradient-text">Your Name</span></h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-400">B.Tech CSE @ VIT Vellore | Data Science @ IITM</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
            <span class="px-4 py-1 glass rounded-full text-sm">Python</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-1 glass rounded-full text-sm">Flutter</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-1 glass rounded-full text-sm">AI/ML</span>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-sky-400">VIT Smart Assistant</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">LLM-powered assistant built with Streamlit and Gemini API for campus navigation and queries.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-500">Python</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-500">Generative AI</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-indigo-400">Rural Health AI</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">WhatsApp-integrated chatbot bridging the gap between rural populations and healthcare services.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-500">SMS/WhatsApp API</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-500">Twilio</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-16">
        <div class="bg-black p-4 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm border border-slate-700">
            <p class="text-green-400">$ system.status()</p>
            <p class="text-slate-300">> CGPA: 8.4 [Optimal]</p>
            <p class="text-slate-300">> Current Task: Preparing for CAT 2 Exams...</p>
            <p class="text-slate-300">> Skills: Data Structures, Multivariable Calculus, C/C++</p>
            <p class="animate-pulse text-sky-400">_</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>